imdb.plot outline: Anna malastas was once a sweet girl that becomes a cruel old woman because of her father's plan of discipline. She inherits a toy company but on a tragic day she got involved in a car accident. She canno't go to heaven because of all the people that she treated wrong but gets a second chance by fixing their current problems. The only problem is she is transformed into her younger self.
